{"tid":1710303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九龍打工仔lunch break快閃遊行】九龍人 做嘢！！！","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:52:59.000Z","uid":45190,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e412f7b915c493123c69d67d7fc4e1611ed0e0c9","tid":1710303,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"【九龍打工仔lunch break快閃遊行】九龍人 做嘢！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［借朋友AC代post］<br />\n中環西裝友OL快閃食彈咁有型，九龍區打工仔唔係唔做啲嘢下話?<br />\n啲人屌唔罷工，但係返左工都可以做啲野！<br />\n吸收左我老母覺得 「 和你返 」 太早好難起身既建議<br />\n犧牲個LUNCH時間，站出來喺街散下步，成本已經係最低！冇理由唔諗下 引D狗出嚟射TG 全世界都要被罷工！！<br />\n建議喺工廠寫字樓區密集嘅地方攪，如觀塘、長沙灣 <br />\n加上地勢上好易成形, 有乜事撤返上OFFICE, 或作後援補給<br />\nD狗唔會夠地頭蛇熟路 我地進可攻 退可守<br />\n人鏈活動好多人參與, 手足人數九龍不比港島少<br />\n應該認真考慮<br />\n<br />\n林鄭話香港人鐘意番工 我地就番佢老母工 罷工係抗爭 返工都係抗爭！！<br />\n不分罷返 罷返合一！！<br />\n<br />\n大家集思廣益，旨在做嘢<br />\n九龍人 做嘢 ！！！！！<br />\n十八區 接力！！！！！ <br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人 報仇！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4294a91256b07b4be4fe3af9f61341040fe64075","tid":1710303,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"62c337ebcff6c5b08e55acfec750fe0be3617660","tid":1710303,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5267e3f3f9875839cb50e389f6e4f8c609e42ddd","tid":1710303,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b3d138d9f985b5be3bac9e41bf6493bb542a6198","tid":1710303,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e61dc744f6